        d="M20 11.8C20 16.2 16.4 19.8 12 19.8C10.8 19.8 9.6 19.5 8.6 19L4.5 20L5.6 16C4.9 14.8 4.5 13.4 4.5 11.8C4.5 7.4 8 3.8 12.4 3.8C16.5 3.8 20 7.3 20 11.8Z"
    />

